				<div class="collapsiblecContent">
					<ul class="circle" style="margin-left: 30px;">
						<li>20 years ago
							<ul class="circle" style="margin-left: 30px;">
								<li>Members of <%=The_Scarlet_Brotherhood%> divined a twin threat to their lineage and purity of their Sule bloodline
									<ul class="circle" style="margin-left: 40px;">
										<li>The recovery of the lost, legendary sword, <%=Zalaam%> &</li>
